reviewText: The content is good, but the dvds often freeze or stop working.
Amazing video from Stan Winston! I have learned so much with the DVDS. I LOVE this line of DVDs.

This DVD is no joke amazing and so worth the investment!! I've learned so much in the 2 1/2 hours I've spent watching this.

If you are looking to learn how to airbrush realistic silicone flesh look no further!!
its the most amazing painting video with airbrush ive ever seen, please buy if you want to be a really good artist.
